{"tid":2167493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周庭畫像全版廣告 由出版反修例運動攝影集及文宣集的團隊「Defiance•Voices」刊登","createTime":"2020-08-21T06:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T07:50:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dbed7562fa019e84f3ed40f4a6f27970cce376a2","tid":2167493,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><a href=\"https://www.defiance-voices-hk.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defiance-voices-hk.com%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4e7e5420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.defiance-voices-hk.com/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/defiance_voices/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdefiance_voices%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=ef296743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/defiance_voices/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/defiancevoices/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdefiancevoices%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=57992b76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/defiancevoices/</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FPaoOyqNfqa9PnfDgEwzzkdxlv0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GBLW2JFPLVCR7DB2ZEDSS5RLAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFPaoOyqNfqa9PnfDgEwzzkdxlv0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGBLW2JFPLVCR7DB2ZEDSS5RLAA.jpg&h=15869a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日《蘋果》A疊共有33則廣告，當中4個為全版廣告，而全版廣告當中，有一個廣告是上周被警方以「港版國安法」拘捕的前香港眾志成員周庭的畫像，畫像上更印上已故美國總統羅斯福名言「The Only Thing We Have To Fear Is Fear Itself（我們唯一要恐懼的就是恐懼本身）」。<br />\n<br />\n該幅全版廣告由出版反修例運動攝影集及文宣集的團隊「Defiance&bull;Voices」刊登，畫像亦是由文宣集《Voices / 吶喊》的總編輯Childe Abaddon所創作。周庭於facebook專頁上表示，雖然事前已經知道和同意刊登廣告，「看到實物，還是有點震撼」，又指對自己的畫像能成為報紙全頁廣告感到受寵若驚，並且感謝各人厚愛，「但同時大家不要忘記，在這片土地上，有很多很多人正在遭受比我更多的痛苦和壓力，他們或許寂寂無名，但卻為了這個家付出了未來。好好支援和支持他們，是我們的責任」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/N2M6AX6SDFCEXBP6KMRGLMUC6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FN2M6AX6SDFCEXBP6KMRGLMUC6A%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=e0e8d9f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FN2M6AX6SDFCEXBP6KMRGLMUC6A%2F&h=cfd9ace7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/N2M6AX6SDFCEXBP6KMRGLMUC6A/</a>"},{"pid":"b5254d086d157704a05da05eb0706accbe761314","tid":2167493,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3aebea841f98a2d7b030f2b094ff2436b34e262","tid":2167493,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5254d086d157704a05da05eb0706accbe761314","tid":2167493,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"